text: Kardeş sen müzik falan yapma be...
text_translated: Brother, don't make music or something...

text: Do you call this music, omg my ears are bleeding...
text_translated: Do you call this music, omg my ears are bleeding...

text: İğrenç olmuş birader bu ne ya, sen buna müzik mi diyorsun
text_translated: It's disgusting bro, what is this, you call it music?

text: Not bad, but not good either...
text_translated: Not bad, but not good either...

text: Really liked this song, please keep up the good work mate :)
text_translated: Really liked this song, please keep up the good work mate :)

text: Gerçekten harika bir şarkı olmuş, sizi tebrik ediyorum, çok beğendim
text_translated: It's really a great song, I congratulate you, I like it very much
